==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Acrogen
<hw>Ac"ro*gen</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'a`kros</grk> extreme, high + <ets>-gen</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A plant of the highest class of cryptogams,
including the ferns, etc. See <er>Cryptogamia</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>The Age of Acrogens</b></col> <fld>(Geol.)</fld>, <cd>the
age of coal plants, or the carboniferous era.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>acrogenic</ent>⟦br⟧
